										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1">马上快到冬至节气了，意味着我们开始步入寒冬，天气也更加干燥，人体也会缺水。应对寒冷干燥的天气，每天吃点水果是非常明智的选择。因为水果当中含有丰富的营养成分，不仅能够很好地滋养肌肤，还能提高身体的免疫力。那么，适合冬至吃的水果有哪些呢？我为你推荐适合冬至时节吃的9种金牌水果，鲜甜多汁营养高，补水滋养又御寒，一起来了解下吧。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-712" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4569f895298a75f3e722a02a5b08e4f6-1024x682.jpg" width="1024" height="682" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4569f895298a75f3e722a02a5b08e4f6-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4569f895298a75f3e722a02a5b08e4f6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4569f895298a75f3e722a02a5b08e4f6-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4569f895298a75f3e722a02a5b08e4f6.jpg 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2"><strong>1、橙子</strong></p>
<p data-track="3">橙子成熟的时候刚好是秋冬季节，水分含量比较足，口感甘甜，对于降燥来说真是不可缺少的水果。橙子不仅含有充分的维生素c，还含有维生素d和维生素a，对人体新陈代谢有明显的调节作用，让身体素质逐渐好转。寒冬里，如果喜欢吃橙又怕生冷，可以做成橙子果酱<strong>，</strong>橙子水果茶，盐蒸橙子等。用叉子戳戳戳果肉，撒一点点盐，拿橙子盖头隔冷水蒸10-15分钟即可，好吃又养生。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-713" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b233c782ed1c3d8a8fe81d5be563173d-1024x686.jpg" width="1024" height="686" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b233c782ed1c3d8a8fe81d5be563173d-1024x686.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b233c782ed1c3d8a8fe81d5be563173d-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b233c782ed1c3d8a8fe81d5be563173d-768x515.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b233c782ed1c3d8a8fe81d5be563173d.jpg 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="4"><strong>2、山楂</strong></p>
<p data-track="5">山楂作为我国传统的药食兼用果品，酸甜可口，颜色喜人，它的维生素C含量同样很高，还含有拥有很强抗氧化能力的黄酮类成分。丰富的果胶对我们的肠道健康也很有好处。山楂的吃法非常多样，除了生吃，还可以制成果脯、山楂糕、点心、糖葫芦、用来泡茶喝，甚至是主食。不过山楂味酸，食用后应及时漱口，以防蛀牙齿。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-714" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0a08d5899480726db070077944be9eb2-1024x682.jpg" width="1024" height="682" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0a08d5899480726db070077944be9eb2-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0a08d5899480726db070077944be9eb2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0a08d5899480726db070077944be9eb2-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0a08d5899480726db070077944be9eb2.jpg 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6"><strong>3、柚子</strong></p>
<p data-track="7">柚子在冬至的时候吃是非常好的，因为柚子的皮很厚，在冬天特别的适合储存，而且它的口感甘酸味道清香，有着“天然维C水果罐头”之称，含丰富的维生素以及多种营养物质，对于上火的人来说，吃柚子能增加体内水分，清热降燥，像这样寒冷的冬季，吃柚子是很理想的选择。</p>
<p data-track="8">柚子全身都是宝，除了直接吃果肉，还可以做成蜂蜜柚子酱，果皮也能做柚子皮糖、柚子皮肉酿等等。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-715" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a578cf2b3e422378878a62c82ffe1fc1-1024x684.jpg" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a578cf2b3e422378878a62c82ffe1fc1-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a578cf2b3e422378878a62c82ffe1fc1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a578cf2b3e422378878a62c82ffe1fc1-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a578cf2b3e422378878a62c82ffe1fc1.jpg 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9"><strong>4、冬枣</strong></p>
<p data-track="10">冬枣是一种在冬天季节比较盛产的枣子，它皮薄肉脆，甘甜清香，深受人们的喜爱，关键还特别有营养！冬枣中维生素C的含量在水果中是名列前茅的，每100克果肉维生素C含量高达380～600毫克，有“活维生素丸”之美誉，而冬至气温低，人很容易受寒气的侵袭导致感冒，常吃冬枣能够帮助提高免疫力，身体好了少感冒。有些人直接吃生的枣会觉得肠胃刺激不舒服，可将冬枣蒸煮泡后再吃也无妨。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-716" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2e05f805d7755b40be3febf34c941ebb-1024x741.jpg" width="1024" height="741" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2e05f805d7755b40be3febf34c941ebb-1024x741.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2e05f805d7755b40be3febf34c941ebb-300x217.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2e05f805d7755b40be3febf34c941ebb-768x556.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2e05f805d7755b40be3febf34c941ebb.jpg 1096w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="11"><strong>5、苹果</strong></p>
<p data-track="12">“每天一个苹果，医生远离我”，苹果是我们生活中最大众的一种水果，也是对人体有好处的水果。苹果里面不仅富含维生素C，还富含苹果酸，鞣酸和柠檬酸等，并且在冬天空气干燥，人的消耗大，代谢慢就更适合吃苹果了。对于一些怕冷、消化不良的人来说，将苹果煮软、蒸软、烤软之后，膳食纤维和果胶变得软化，对肠胃刺激比较小，这样更容易被人体吸收。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-717" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4dbc1c8549fae6b96fcb27f9e0fd90fe.jpg" width="974" height="651" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4dbc1c8549fae6b96fcb27f9e0fd90fe.jpg 974w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4dbc1c8549fae6b96fcb27f9e0fd90fe-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4dbc1c8549fae6b96fcb27f9e0fd90fe-768x513.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 974px) 100vw, 974px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="13"><strong>6、甘蔗</strong></p>
<p data-track="14">甘蔗与其他水果不同，它是一种植物的茎，冬至干燥，特别适合吃甘蔗，它的水分含量很高，其中的蔗糖、葡萄糖及果糖含量高达12%。同时它还可以作为清凉的补剂，有滋补清热的作用。甘蔗除了直接削皮后吃外，还可以用它榨汁喝，还可以切小段，搭配马蹄、胡萝卜等清润食材一起煮着喝，简单又健康的糖水。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-718" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3dfeb2aa8feeaa234d993af4f8399571.jpg" width="974" height="653" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3dfeb2aa8feeaa234d993af4f8399571.jpg 974w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3dfeb2aa8feeaa234d993af4f8399571-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3dfeb2aa8feeaa234d993af4f8399571-768x515.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 974px) 100vw, 974px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="15"><strong>7、橘子</strong></p>
<p data-track="16">橘子也是人们最爱吃的水果之一。橘子果肉酸甜适中，水分多，富有香气，它的果肉、果皮、果核都有一定的药用价值，可以说全身是宝。它含大量维生素C、枸橼酸及葡萄糖等十余种营养物质，橘肉除了生吃，还可以做成果酱，适当吃橘子可以帮助人们生津开胃。不过需要注意的是，橘子性温，属于热性水果，吃太多容易上火。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-719" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8d0b0a05b16fda813f30d1d8a6d44048-1024x689.jpg" width="1024" height="689" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8d0b0a05b16fda813f30d1d8a6d44048-1024x689.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8d0b0a05b16fda813f30d1d8a6d44048-300x202.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8d0b0a05b16fda813f30d1d8a6d44048-768x517.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8d0b0a05b16fda813f30d1d8a6d44048.jpg 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="17"><strong>8、香蕉</strong></p>
<p data-track="18">香蕉营养高、热量低，是相当好的营养食品。香蕉香甜软糯，几乎含有所有的维生素、食物纤维和钾、镁、钠等矿物质，能令皮肤光润细滑，特别是冬天的人因为寒冷干燥，常常容易大便秘结，香蕉能够很好的促进肠道消化功能，并且多吃香蕉能够很好的调节心情，令人快乐开心。</p>
<p data-track="19">如果嫌香蕉太冰冷不喜欢吃，香蕉也是可以加热吃的，在米粥将熟的时候，放入适量香蕉块，至粥熟即成香蕉粥，美味又健康。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-720" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/fc03a76565ddc25579005178da3f740a.jpg" width="969" height="646" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/fc03a76565ddc25579005178da3f740a.jpg 969w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/fc03a76565ddc25579005178da3f740a-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/fc03a76565ddc25579005178da3f740a-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 969px) 100vw, 969px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="20"><strong>9、猕猴桃</strong></p>
<p data-track="21">猕猴桃是猕猴最爱吃的一种，故名为猕猴桃。每年的秋末冬初正是猕猴桃成熟的季节，这时的猕猴桃肉质丰厚，果肉细嫩，入口即化，营养价值也非常高。猕猴桃的维生素C含量极高，每个人一天吃半个猕猴桃，便能满足人体全天维生素C的需求量，此外，它叶酸的含量也极高，还有胡萝卜素等各种营养素，被誉为“水果之王”。</p>
